"他们的领袖移动到那个村庄里了！他没有我所想的那么愚蠢。村庄每回合都会为他治"
"疗，而且会提供很好的防御（闪避）。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1312
msgid ""
"That unit has captured our village! You’d better get him out; it heals him "
"each turn and provides good defense."
